title: 14. Navigating Self Doubt
description:
Hey Girl Hey!

 

Do you ever doubt yourself and your abilities? Ever feel like you can't move past it or every time you try to move past it the thoughts in your head keep you from achieving what you set out to do? Tune in to this week's episode to find out how you can navigate and work through self doubt!

Click here to get my new e-book the 3 Steps to Radical Self Forgiveness

...or click here to get a preview first :) 

Please don't forget to rate & review!
